{
  "page": "Lord of Tarth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Tarth</b> is the title given to head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\">House Tarth</a> whose castle is <a href=\"/index.php/Evenfall_Hall\" title=\"Evenfall Hall\">Evenfall Hall</a>, they rule the Island of <a href=\"/index.php/Tarth\" title=\"Tarth\">Tarth</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Selwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Selwyn Tarth\">Selwyn Tarth</a> is the current holder of that title.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Tarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Evenfall\" title=\"Lord of Evenfall\">Lord of Evenfall</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Evenstar\" title=\"Evenstar\">Evenstar</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Tarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7